(3, 'Yogi Approved Classes', 'The title speaks for itself: Not only are you getting a great price for top-notch, customized programs, all of which have a goal â€” like healing or chakra-awakening â€” but you\'re also giving back. For every class you stream, YogaApproved, along with Trees for the Future, plants one tree in a country that can benefit from the agriculture. Plus, the service is convenient, especially if you feel uncomfortable in a yoga studio or want to practice your handstands in the comfort of your own home.', 'Not into exhilarating HIIT workouts? Look no further than Ballet Beautiful\'s fitness method, created by former New York City Ballet professional Mary Helen Bowers. The transformative exercise embodies the grace and artistry of ballet, while building long, lean, and strong muscles. Don\'t worry â€” you don\'t have to be at Black Swan level to leap into this exercise program (although Mary Helen did personally train Natalie Portman for the international blockbuster).', '3 - 6 months', 'pro10.jfif', 'Ed The Machine'),
(4, 'Peloton Digital', 'If you love cycling as much as we do, you might already have your own bike at home or are considering adding one to your home gym. Now, you can stream energetic spin classes so you can work it out at home or in a hotel (many hotels now have Peloton bikes) whenever you want. Aside from cycling, there are other countless classes offered in running, bootcamp, and even outdoor workouts. All of the classes are taught by elite NYC instructors, so you can dive right into a challenging studio experience at any time.', 'Aside from cycling, there are other countless classes offered in running, bootcamp, and even outdoor workouts. All of the classes are taught by elite NYC instructors, so you can dive right into a challenging studio experience at any time.', '6 - 9 months', 'pro2.jfif', 'Ed The Machine'),
(5, 'Crush60 Complete Package', 'Founded by 26-year-old Ben Williamson in 2014, Crush Fitness launched to provide everyone (from the weary weightlifter to avid gymgoer) with a program that was both affordable and effective. Drawing an impressive social media fan base, the brand has since expanded from one to four innovative programs that can be used at the gym, at home, and with a variety of exercises you can implement into your personal routine.', 'The original Crush60 package comes with a 60-day, three-phase instructional guide, with hand-drawn illustrations and video embeds for reference. It includes a nutritional guide as well, so you\'ll not only be successful in the gym, but also learn to make healthier choices in the kitchen.', '7 - 9 months', 'pro3.jfif', 'Esta Morenikeji'),
(6, 'Daily Burns', 'Intimidated by the gym? We totally get it. The good news is that you can absolutely stay within your comfort zone and still stay fit. Daily Burn is your one-stop cyber-shop to 30-minute workouts you can do right at home! We love the variety of routines to experiment with almost as much as we admire the Daily Burn community. Members enjoy an on-demand library of more than 150 workouts â€” from yoga and cardio to strength- and body-training.', 'Daily Burn is your one-stop cyber-shop to 30-minute workouts you can do right at home! We love the variety of routines to experiment with almost as much as we admire the Daily Burn community. Members enjoy an on-demand library of more than 150 workouts â€” from yoga and cardio to strength- and body-training.', '3 - 6 months', 'pro4.jfif', 'Joshua Paul'),
(7, 'Physique57 On-Demand Streaming', 'Amazingly solid muscle tone awaits with Physique57\'s interval overload workout. Get access to six preset programs, in addition to other videos, where you use your body as your main source of resistance through thigh-burning squats, toning arm exercises, and chiseling ab moves. If you have access to equipment, they show you how to incorporate the basic tools. Raise the barre with any of their streamed workouts.', 'For most of us, exercise probably has to be squeezed in between the priorities of carting kids to school, meal prepping, and getting to work on time. No one\'s perfect, and the interactive online community reminds you that that\'s OK, and they\'ll support your efforts toward becoming your best self.', '3 - 6 months', 'pro5.jfif', 'Joshua Paul'),
(8, 'SWEAT by Kayla Itsines', 'The Sweat With Kayla movement exploded across Instagram, and if you\'ve yet to join Itsines\' army, just mulling over a few of her photos and videos (she even did her regular workouts while almost 9 months pregnant!) will get you on board. We\'re not about sugarcoating: Her programs are tough, but you\'re going to love them anyway. Designed for women of all shapes and sizes and for all levels of fitness, the workout programs range from post-pregnancy to powerbuilding, and can be done at home or the actual gym! The app also provides users with weekly clean-eating meal plans and shopping lists.', 'Designed for women of all shapes and sizes and for all levels of fitness, the workout programs range from post-pregnancy to powerbuilding, and can be done at home or the actual gym! The app also provides users with weekly clean-eating meal plans and shopping lists.', '6 - 8 months', 'pro6.jfif', 'Ekemini Ekerette'),
(9, 'CorePower Yoga', 'Access a collection of online classes for all yoga abilities through CorePower Yoga\'s Yoga On Demand program. New classes will be added every week, and users can access the entire library for free. If you\'re new to CorePower, it\'s designed as a high-intensity yoga class with targeted core exercises throughout the workout. Give a class a try to take your yoga practice up a notch.', 'If you\'re new to CorePower, it\'s designed as a high-intensity yoga class with targeted core exercises throughout the workout. Give a class a try to take your yoga practice up a notch.', '7 - 9 months', 'pro7.jfif', 'Damola Ladejobi'),
(10, 'YogaWorks Online Yoga Class', 'In yoga, practice makes perfect, and you can go at your own pace. YogaWorks allows you to do so with the help of more than 40 professional instructors and more than 30 Journey Series that target specific areas of the body or working toward a particular pose. You\'ll also get an unlimited, all-access pass to 950-plus premium classes stored on your computer or mobile device. They understand that while your schedule may not be flexible, it\'s possible for you to be, which is why this service is so popular. With some classes as short as 10 minutes, you can stream it anywhere, anytime, at your convenience.', 'You\'ll also get an unlimited, all-access pass to 950-plus premium classes stored on your computer or mobile device. They understand that while your schedule may not be flexible, it\'s possible for you to be, which is why this service is so popular. With some classes as short as 10 minutes, you can stream it anywhere, anytime, at your convenience.', '1 year', 'pro8.jfif', 'Victor Paul'),
(11, 'Alo Moves Multi-Class Series', 'Find the yoga class that\'s right for you. Alo Moves, a platform developed by trendy activewear brand Alo Yoga, makes choosing your class a totally chill experience. You can easily sort through different class lengths (from 15 minutes to 60 minutes) or choose from a variety of experience levels, from beginner to advanced. You can even select intensity levels no matter your experience, so you can still push your limits as a beginner or take it easy on a rest day as a seasoned yogi.', 'The world-class instructors will guide you through Hatha-, Ashtanga-, or Vinyasa-style yoga, meditations, poses and techniques, and more. There are even categories specifically for enhancing flexibility and building strength, so it\'s truly a one-stop shop!', '1 year', 'pro9.jfif', 'Maje Ayida'),
(12, 'All Out Studio', 'All Out Studio offers instant workouts from the worldâ€™s most respected fitness brands, all in one place â€“ Menâ€™s Health, Womenâ€™s Health, Prevention, Runnerâ€™s World, and more. The workouts are for all levels, all goals, and all bodies. Youâ€™ll find everything from kettle bell workouts to high intensity dance cardio, yoga, and full-body strength training. These celebrity trainers donâ€™t often share their secrets, but they do for All Out Studioâ€™s app.', 'The workouts are for all levels, all goals, and all bodies. Youâ€™ll find everything from kettle bell workouts to high intensity dance cardio, yoga, and full-body strength training. These celebrity trainers donâ€™t often share their secrets, but they do for All Out Studioâ€™s app.', '3 - 6 months', 'pro1.jfif', 'Bunmi George'),
(13, 'Caravan Wellness', 'Looking for a more holistic approach, but can\'t afford a personal trainer, nutritionist, and life coach? Check out Caravan Wellness, a curated fitness destination with a wide range of both unlimited live and on-demand classes and short tips (such as a quick how-to on mindful eating or gut health), ranging from yoga and meditation to Pilates and life coaching that you can watch anywhere. You can even talk goals, technique, and progress on your time with their pro teachers and coaches through the built-in messaging system.', 'You can dance away your stress on a literal trampoline with Body By Simone\'s high energy, high-intensity dance cardio mixed with a strength-training workout. The quick, 10-to-20 minute program uses your body weight in addition to lightweight resistance to develop long, lean muscles. The technique grew out of creator Simone De La Rue\'s classical ballet and Broadway background, and has taken flight since her launch in 2010. Now with a subscription, you can stream it online to any device, including your TV.', '6 - 9 months', 'pro4.jfif', 'Buchi Okereke');

